  "description": "Numerical pilot for Brownian motion and gravitational sedimentation of diamond particles in aqueous suspension. The v0.4 release closes program-context slices S3 (citation-anchored hydrodynamic-shell calibration per FND class) and S5 (concentration-weighted polydispersity kernel with per-regime conditional radius moments), hardens parallel walk_grid under macOS spawn-context, and adds a parameter-sweep root-finder. Zero-default paths reproduce v0.3 arithmetic to machine precision.",
